    "body": "### Problem\n\nRelated  https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/19741\n\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/neovim/comments/1g8bqut/diagnostic_severity_sort_doesnt_apply_to_underline/\n\nRight now the `vim.diagnostic.Opts.severity_sort` does not sort `underline` hl\n\n<details>\n<summary>img</summary>\n\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d51728e5-6e0d-43bd-81a2-3521f00d66f6)\n\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n`severity_sort` would sort all diagnostic information (underline, virtual_text)\n\n<details>\n<summary>img</summary>\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/99fb401a-2078-4009-8f79-8cc0827f96c2)\n\n</details>\n\n",
